Thus, a possible implementation for decryption is (using PHP/OpenSSL): 

```php
$key = &quot;12345&quot;;
$ciphertext = &quot;84b24172c57752385251d142abadbed1d9945301a3aee429ce00c1e291a605c30ad18c5e00007f6db394fc6138a2ee4c&quot;;
